{"tid":1844543,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"涉妨礙住戶進入大廈累少年被捕　華明邨女保安遭即炒","createTime":"2020-01-26T16:18:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-26T20:05:52.000Z","uid":3204,"like":404,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":105,"replies":[{"pid":"71d437c6a83a17c6cae779351d2f3c51b49d1101","tid":1844543,"uid":3204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T16:18:37.000Z","msg":"【涉妨礙住戶進入大廈累少年被捕　華明邨女保安遭即炒】<br />\n<br />\n今日（1月26日）下午起，大批粉嶺居民在新落成的暉明邨外圍聚集，不滿政府考慮將該邨改裝為臨時居所，視乎需要給予沒有病徵的緊密接觸者作隔離觀察。<br />\n<br />\n入夜之後，有人在暉明邨路口以雜物及磚頭堵路，亦有人向大廈大堂掟汽油彈，結果大批防暴警察到場，有部分人士散到去附近的華明邨。<br />\n<br />\n消息指，有大廈女保安於警方到場時，拒絕讓住客進入，結果令一名住客被捕，有居於附近華明邨的居民不滿，指罵涉事的女保安員，女保安員當場嚎哭，要由高層安慰。<br />\n<br />\n涉事的保安公司晚上發出通告，指「就2020年1月26日晚上懷疑有保安員妨礙住戶進入富明樓，本公司已即時嚴肅處理，該員工已違反公司工作指引，已即時將該名保安員終止僱員合約」。<br />\n<br />\n全文︰<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/01-26-2020/59381\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F01-26-2020%2F59381&d=0fPPgjUU32Qc%2B%2Bj2t4ropLQTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=90537e75\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/01-26-2020/59381</a>"},{"pid":"a7fc97c8f0b2fa4665fb5b8e8b6fbedfe7e665a2","tid":1844543,"uid":264245,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T16:18:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rHg8fGB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrHg8fGB.png&h=077d795f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSolomon都有講話禁止中國航班飛美國，不過要請佢留意埋香港：<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SolomonYue/status/1221454591335653377\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSolomonYue%2Fstatus%2F1221454591335653377&d=0fPPgjUU32Qc%2B%2Bj2t4ropLQTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=d85c8739\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSolomonYue%2Fstatus%2F1221454591335653377&h=ce7d6a4e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SolomonYue/status/1221454591335653377</a><br />\n國際戰線：求國際封鎖香港<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=