re":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T16:48:56.000Z","msg":"間公司做得幾好"},{"pid":"9cd42bedb24032ea640c2473c35f188fb59c2905","tid":1844543,"uid":88022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T16:49:09.000Z","msg":"做乜新年流流炒我呀<br />\n等咗成年呢幾日就三糧架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n開鳩佢名<br />\n逗完利是反轉豬肚唔認人<br />\n養到你看門口肥肥白白 反咬主子一口"},{"pid":"0391b9e396ffb04c17b8ec8675a1e56a74f87157","tid":1844543,"uid":269967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T16:49:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76a4bc1daa0d10d064cf9cd4106fa0608ebac42d","tid":1844543,"uid":280886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79147135d2f755dd058c25a8f1d0659d02dd19d5","tid":1844543,"uid":68598,"like":81,"dislike":0,"score":81,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T16:21:47.000Z","msg":"都要起底 <br />\n俾佢做第個屋苑仲得了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T16:54:28.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"ccb13d6d6030c8734edcb26b1c08284cf3fd29d1","tid":1844543,"uid":280886,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"eb1faffe9c532355eb440ab5d1e7fb0f6b580054","tid":1844543,"uid":326037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71d437c6a83a17c6cae779351d2f3c51b49d1101","tid":1844543,"uid":3204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T16:18:37.000Z","msg":"【涉妨礙住戶進入大廈累少年被捕　華明邨女保安遭即炒】<br />\n<br />\n今日（1月26日）下午起，大批粉嶺居民在新落成的暉明邨外圍聚集，不滿政府考慮將該邨改裝為臨時居所，視乎需要給予沒有病徵的緊密接觸者作隔離觀察。<br />\n<br />\n入夜之後，有人在暉明邨路口以雜物及磚頭堵路，亦有人向大廈大堂掟汽油彈，結果大批防暴警察到場，有部分人士散到去附近的華明邨。<br />\n<br />\n消息指，有大廈女保安於警方到場時，拒絕讓住客進入，結果令一名住客被捕，有居於附近華明邨的居民不滿，指罵涉事的女保安員，女保安員當場嚎哭，要由高層安慰。<br />\n<br />\n涉事的保安公司晚上發出通告，指「就2020年1月26日晚上懷疑有保安員妨礙住戶進入富明樓，本公司已即時嚴肅處理，該員工已違反公司工作指引，已即時將該名保安員終止僱員合約」。<br />\n<br />\n全文︰<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/01-26-2020/59381\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F01-26-2020%2F59381&d=0fPPgjUU32Qc%2B%2Bj2t4ropLQTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=90537e75\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/01-26-2020/59381</a>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T16:22:50.000Z","msg":"保安好易揾工，大把藍保安公司請番佢啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T16:56:52.000Z","msg":"所以一定要起佢個樣<br />\n見親佢做就投訴！"},{"pid":"f36b53b62d360bcdf84d5cac625db45e09ca962c","tid":1844543,"uid":312076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79147135d2f755dd058c25a8f1d0659d02dd19d5","tid":1844543,"uid":68598,"like":81,"dislike":0,"score":81,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T16:21:47.000Z","msg":"都要起底 <br />\n俾佢做第個屋苑仲得了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T16:59:17.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"e36374beb809fe9b38d71935168e7fb04788d5da","tid":1844543,"uid":264872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d8afafe9d600ad1109c63b9a5b37b25f21768b55","tid":1844543,"uid":104138,"like":89,"dislike":4,"score":85,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T16:21:03.000Z","msg":"抵死，車公講得無錯，即時現眼報"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T17:01:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19ce0510dd61b5fa07b255d1a6a6bd2e2f3c333c","tid":1844543,"uid":66346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T17:03:08.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"0a09fada8842d1600c5f26e8bc27a3fbdb7049d8","tid":1844543,"uid":170987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79147135d2f755dd058c25a8f1d0659d02dd19d5","tid":1844543,"uid":68598,"like":81,"dislike":0,"score":81,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T16:21:47.000Z","msg":"都要起底 <br />\n俾佢做第個屋苑仲得了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T17:03:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6e36a439e874dbe9cb6c6147bf65a5913d980f68","tid":1844543,"uid":147721,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T17:04:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/fac